data.description: Don't miss out on this remarkable home in the Golden Gate City area! Conveniently close to I-75, Stunning gulf coast beaches, downtown Naples, and more, this property boasts a spacious fenced backyard, ideal for gatherings, kids' play, pets or simply enjoying the Florida ambiance while savoring your morning coffee in the closed serene lanai.   Featuring three bedrooms, two baths, tiled flooring throughout, fully renovated kitchen, and master bath, this home offers comfort and style. The converted garage serves as a fourth bedroom with its own entrance, perfect for independent family members seeking privacy.  With a 2023 roof, gutters, soffit, and fresh exterior paint, along with newer appliances that enhance both flair and practicality in the kitchen, this residence exemplifies the quintessential Florida lifestyle. Seize this opportunity to make it your own!
